<div class="box"></div>
    <h2 class="title">Recovery password</h2>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <b>{{email}},</b></p>

            <div class="info">
				<p>We received a request to reset your password for your Copute account. To reset your password, please click the link below.</p>
                <p>{{link}}</p>
				<p>Please note that this link is valid for 30 minutes. If you do not reset your password within this time, you will need to request a new link.</p>
                <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email, and your account will remain secure.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
